<h1>Reset your password</h1>

<p>
  Click the button below to reset your password <br> 
  <%= button_to "Reset your password", edit_password_reset_url(@user.password_reset_token), class: "btn btn-primary" %>

  If the button is not working, just copy and paste the link below in your browser:
  <%= edit_password_url(@user.password_reset_token) %>
  <strong>If you did not request your password to be reset please ignore this email.</strong>
</p>
